  This should live above the site chrome so it covers the full width of the browser.

  ## block usage
  The component yields blocks at each level.

  ## yields
  key name | yields | description
  --- | --- | ---
  `.header` | `.left`, `.right` | two flex blocks with laid out with `justify-content: speace-between`.
  `.left` | `.logos` | left side of the top bar
  `.logos` | N/A | list of NYPR network logos rendered as SVGs with links
  `.right` |  `.button` | right side of the top bar
  `.button` | N/A | a button that opens the `burger-menu` when clicked
"}}

